<h3 id="三、监控与运维-确保锁机制稳定运行" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#三、监控与运维-确保锁机制稳定运行"><span>三、监控与运维：确保锁机制稳定运行</span></a></h3>
<h4 id="_3-1-锁监控-关键指标实时告警" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-1-锁监控-关键指标实时告警"><span>3.1 锁监控：关键指标实时告警</span></a></h4>
<p>淘票票通过<RouteLink to="/zh/series/myprojects/%E6%B7%98%E7%A5%A8%E7%A5%A8/%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E9%94%81/blogs/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/Prometheus.html">Prometheus</RouteLink>+<RouteLink to="/zh/series/myprojects/%E6%B7%98%E7%A5%A8%E7%A5%A8/%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E9%94%81/blogs/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/Grafana.html">Grafana</RouteLink>搭建分布式锁监控体系，实时监控锁的关键指标，异常时触发告警（如钉钉、邮件），避免锁机制“暗箱操作”。</p>
<h4 id="核心监控指标" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#核心监控指标"><span>核心监控指标</span></a></h4>
